,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b77822185169648a5a69167c2dbac6b47a2e5e3","tid":1710492,"uid":36048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:41:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0e219b96d3255c4ba2c18a9be417f3e30c60077","tid":1710492,"uid":202534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"救cu啊!<br />\n<br />\n⚠⚠⚠!!!! 重要 !!! ⚠⚠⚠<br />\n<br />\n目前中大 極度須要支援 唔理係人手定物資定子彈<br />\n<br />\n可以趕去既手足請火速支援<br />\n<br />\n⚠⚠⚠!!!!前線須求!!! ⚠⚠⚠<br />\n泳鏡 玻璃樽 毛巾 可投式物品 少量食物 飲用水 寶礦力 雀巢咖啡等<br />\n豬嘴 有濾棉無嘴啊中大<br />\n要Ice pad 海量first aid物質<br />\nIce pad&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;紗布繃帶&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;鹽水<br />\n<br />\n現時暫時車未必入到黎，<br />\n由於東鐵線介乎大埔墟至火炭站服務暫停，乘客若要前往中文大學，可乘搭以下路線<br />\n馬鞍山：87k、807A、807K、807C<br />\n大水坑：289K<br />\n<br />\n或者聯絡CUSU接收物資，暴大要<br />\n<br />\n學生活動中心設置物資站，唯現存物資如長傘、水、急救物資皆短缺<br />\n- 歡迎同學可擺放相關物資於學生活動中心, (女工旁），或收集散落中大校園的物資予本會"},{"pid":"bc8685862fb781cbce0d1f4515bd236a3b31ca70","tid":1710492,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:43:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c2c269f826dbc329a62db96942d96266fe9fa028","tid":1710492,"uid":176743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a73ae1215d8c35baaa564610ba27bddbf21e001","tid":1710492,"uid":36048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:45:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a90e957d790b7157d912463f47c8232e232f5d6b","tid":1710492,"uid":36048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:45:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fed6448200a309aab80d6245d824b7ad65ba76f","tid":1710492,"uid":311022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0804fced774ab746a1a90209e00d1759f1f21dcf","tid":1710492,"uid":186096,"like":